::KitKat::

She smiled at him. "Good."  She tried not to show that she was 
worrried for him.  But she was.  She went up to the maximal. "You got 
5 seconds to get out of this base before I kill you myself.  And I'm 
counting.  1......" she pointed to the entrance and motioned for him 
to leave.  "2........"  She waited for him to run, even though she 
was  right next to him, she moved so as not to block him and waited 
for himt o run for it.
